Armed Forces Veterans Hubs
During the past 12 months, an increasing need for new Veterans Hubs and Drop-in
centres has been identified with many Ex-Service and Veterans experiencing loneliness
and depression.
The Nepalese Community Centre exclusively in Cheriton, Shorncliffe - continues to do well
and is especially important because KCC played a part in supporting the local Nepalese
Community taking on a lease from KCC to open and run the Community Centre, which is
part of Cheriton Library.

